    "causal_summary": "Phase 010 implements pt-03 RQ-B5 client extraction. Extracts shared RerankClient<T> + EmbeddingCacheClient interfaces from memory cross-encoder + embedding-cache; CocoIndex opt-in adapter for rerank only. NO shared persistent storage (Voyage Code 3 vs Voyage 4 model_id binding). NO shared indexing pipelines (SKIP boundary binding). Cross-backend hit-rate overlap telemetry feeds future shared-store decision. Foundational interface for future RQ-A5 fusion consumer (when Phases 001-003 ship). Dependency added for the Coco adapter path: Phase 001 must land before this phase modifies mcp-coco-index; the memory-only interface extraction can still be reasoned about independently.",
